and the UAE witnessed remarkable developments. HH Sheikh Mohamed Bin Rashid Al-Maktoum, UAE Vice-President, Prime Minister and Ruler of Dubai, states in the preface: \u201c\u2026Tradesmen in both countries have played a significant role in building cultural, social and commercial bridges between their peoples. Such developments have placed India at the forefront of commercial and industrial exchange with the UAE, in addition to other non-petroleum industries.\u201d The 267-page book contains five chapters: a historical review of the long-standing relations between India and the UAE; the scope of their political relations; a comprehensive review of economic activity; relations in the fields of health and education; and finally, on the people in both India and the UAE. India and the UAE: In Celebration of a Legendary Friendship is supported with scores of pictures, illustrations, maps and tables collected by the author from various sources, including the National Archives (NA).<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3962,"template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false},"product_cat":[15],"product_tag":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3961"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3962"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3961"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3961"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.nla.ae\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3961"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}